屌9你"},{"pid":"72eed5638690687b9f9856214d2c721c45687b2d","tid":1069603,"uid":107408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司ot好似理所當然<br />\n有日準時收工仲會比人問做咩今日咁早走"},{"pid":"ccd228aac0981e867770af501e72f7074c515252","tid":1069603,"uid":40624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"又係戇鳩晴報"},{"pid":"b64d99dfda75354563e275e33c2a52ef390c6988","tid":1069603,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T13:33:55.000Z","msg":"OT有錢收都唔太想O<br />\n想休息下"},{"pid":"f6d014922da518aab744204f614c46e4df2066ee","tid":1069603,"uid":7363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:04:14.000Z","msg":"戇撚鳩，幾時變咗準時放工都係罪過，奴港真係冇改錯名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bc4e9f64a4d00996514fdbf165d4033b9312a5","tid":1069603,"uid":159333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:09:11.000Z","msg":"有無歸屬感關你鬼事咩<br />\n做到野咪得囉<br />\n合約寫明辦公時間<br />\n準時走先有合約精神<br />\n如果ot一分鐘你都計返比我就唔同講法<br />\n均均真真好"},{"pid":"9055f0f209ff607f9234aa4593d81547fedfe577","tid":1069603,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T14:13:37.000Z","msg":"咁好心就明買明賣<br />\ncontract寫8點收，如果我簽得實唔會有怨言架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}